OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA settled
OL,6,Fand mostly clear night with the wind
OL,7,Fremaining light. Mild in urban areas,
OL,8,Fcooler in rural spots allowing patchy
OL,9,Ffog or mist to form in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAnother hot day with
OL,12,Ftemperatures continuing to rise. Dry
OL,13,Fand sunny with the wind remaining
OL,14,Flight.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,17,Fand sunny with light winds on Monday
OL,18,Fand Tuesday. Staying hot on Monday and
OL,19,FTuesday with temperatures starting to
OL,20,Ffall a little by Wednesday, especially
OL,21,Fin eastern parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
